          "target": "如果链接的经文有误，请更改此项。例如，您想要“创 1,1-3”但输出的是第 2-4 节的文本 → 请将此项设置为 -1"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "If set, only headings of specified level are considered verses (if first heading of this level is always a verse, also set \"Verse offset\" to -1)",
