        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "String inserted in front of every line, for example '>' for quote. Note: If you set 'Put each verse on a new line?' to true, the prefix will be inserted in front of every line.",
          "target": "插入在每行前面的字符串，例如用于引用的 '>'。注意：如果将“每节经文放在新行？”设置为 true，该前缀将插入到每行前面。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "String inserted after biblical link, you can use \\n to insert newline. If you are using multiple translations \"{t}\" will insert the name of the one used.",
          "target": "插入在圣经链接后面的字符串，您可以使用 \\\\n 插入换行符。如果您使用多个译本，“{t}”将插入所使用的译本名称。"
        },
